<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākābdē nāgaratnāruṇaparigaṇitē rādāmāsē
<lb n="2"/>śitāyāṁ saptamyāṁ śaurivarē hariśikharipatēssaṁnidhau dīpa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>dīptyai <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> prādādācaṁdratāraṁ <unclear>vi</unclear>yadiṣaṁgaṇitā naicikīḥ pu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṇyasidyai svargāstyai ca svapitrōḥ prakaṭitaguṇavāneṟṟayā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>matyavaryya<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśakavarṣaṁbulu 1298 gunēṁṭi vaiśakha
<lb n="6"/>śukla saptamiyu śanivāramunāṁḍu kāsyapagōtrajuṁḍaina
<lb n="7"/>Oḍḍādi Aḍuva venamapegaḍa koḍuku Eṟṟayapegaḍa tama talli
<lb n="8" break="no"/>daṁḍrulakuṁ buṇyalōkaprāptigānu tanaku Iṣṭartthasiddhigānu
<lb n="9"/>śrīnarasihanāduni sannadini nityamunnu Oka Akhaṁḍadīpamu
<lb n="10"/>veluṁguṭakuṁ beṭṭina <unclear>mō</unclear>dālu Eṁbai 50 Ī mōdālaṁ gaci
<lb n="11"/>kāḷasakaḷabōyuṁḍu māsapaḍi neyi Ēḍu guṁcālu
<lb n="12" break="no"/>nnu reṁḍu vīsalu teci śrībhaṁḍāramaṁduṁ bravēśamu cēyaṁga
<lb n="13" break="no"/>lāṁ<unclear>ḍu</unclear> dīpapratima Okaṭi <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dharmmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrīśrīśrī
</p>

